Classical mechanics was position, momenta, Euler-Lagrange equations.
 Hamilton's equations
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\dot{p}=-\frac{dH}{dq}\quad\quad\dot{q}=\frac{dH}{dp}
\]

\end_inset


